<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idef81a3db-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s2328"><num value="2328">§ 2328.</num><heading> Library</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary shall maintain a library of scientific and other works and periodicals, both foreign and domestic, in the Plant Variety Protection Office to aid the examiners in the discharge of their duties.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idef81a3dc-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/pl/91/577/tI/s8">Pub. L. 91–577, title I, § 8</ref>, <date date="1970-12-24">Dec. 24, 1970</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/84/1543">84 Stat. 1543</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/96/574/s3">Pub. L. 96–574, § 3</ref>, <date date="1980-12-22">Dec. 22, 1980</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/94/3350">94 Stat. 3350</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
